HEADWORD: Concurring
<hw>Con*cur"ring</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<def>Agreeing.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Concurring figure</b></col> <fld>(Geom.)</fld>, <cd>one
which, being laid on another, exactly meets every part of it, or one
which corresponds with another in all its parts.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Concuss</ent>⟦br⟧
